This branch contains Containerfile for building the container with the XEyes GUI app

============================================
# HOW TO PREPARE THE CONSTAINER FOR PRODUCTION

podman build -f containerfile

============================================
# GENERAL HELP

Build with:
  podman build -f containerfile

Tag the image (assign name to it):
  podman tag <hash> <name>

Run the GUI container with:
  podman run -d -v /tmp/.X11-unix:/tmp/.X11-unix -e DISPLAY=:0 <hash>

Attach to the running conatiner (output) with:
  podman attach <hash>

Connect to the conatiner independently why it runs:
  podman exec -ti <hash> bash

============================================
